sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Platform Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant WVA as WVA Controller Manager
    participant SatEngine as Saturation Engine<br/>(60s interval)
    participant SFZEngine as Scale-from-Zero Engine
    participant Prom as Prometheus / Thanos<br/>9090-9091/TCP HTTPS
    participant Metrics as WVA /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant HPAKEDA as HPA / KEDA
    participant Targets as Deployments / LWS

    Note over Admin,Targets: Flow 1: Saturation-Based Autoscaling Decision

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create VariantAutoscaling CR<br/>(model, scale target, variant cost)
    K8sAPI->>WVA: Informer: VA CR event
    WVA->>WVA: Reconcile: register variant<br/>in DecisionCache

    loop Every 60s (GLOBAL_OPT_INTERVAL)
        SatEngine->>Prom: PromQL: vllm_kv_cache_usage,<br/>vllm_queue_depth, request_rates<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
        Prom-->>SatEngine: Metrics response (cached w/ TTL)
        SatEngine->>SatEngine: SaturationV2Analyzer:<br/>compute optimal replicas<br/>(KV cache threshold=0.80,<br/>queue threshold=5)
        SatEngine->>SatEngine: Greedy optimizer:<br/>allocate cheapest variant first,<br/>remove most expensive
        SatEngine->>SatEngine: Store decisions in DecisionCache
        SatEngine->>Metrics: Emit wva_optimal_replicas,<br/>wva_saturation metrics
    end

    Prom->>Metrics: Scrape /metrics<br/>Auth: Bearer Token + SAR
    Metrics-->>Prom: WVA optimization metrics
    HPAKEDA->>Prom: Query custom metrics<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Prom-->>HPAKEDA: wva_optimal_replicas
    HPAKEDA->>K8sAPI: Patch scale subresource<br/>Auth: SA Token
    K8sAPI->>Targets: Scale replicas

    Note over Admin,Targets: Flow 2: Scale-from-Zero

    K8sAPI->>SFZEngine: Informer: InferencePool CR event
    SFZEngine->>SFZEngine: Detect pending requests<br/>on pool with 0 replicas
    SFZEngine->>K8sAPI: Patch Deployment/LWS replicas<br/>(0 → minReplicas)<br/>Auth: SA Token
    K8sAPI->>Targets: Scale from zero

    Note over Admin,Targets: Flow 3: Dynamic Configuration Update

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Update ConfigMap<br/>(saturation thresholds)
    K8sAPI->>WVA: Informer: ConfigMap event<br/>(labeled app.kubernetes.io/name:<br/>workload-variant-autoscaler)
    WVA->>WVA: ConfigMapReconciler:<br/>update thresholds live<br/>(no pod restart)
